Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier  而那也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.24,0:00:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.51,0:00:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同时站在火线的两端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.15,0:00:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绕过危险的转角  追过生与死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.59,0:00:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑战谎言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.52,0:00:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论编织出多少谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.20,0:00:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相还是会照出光明的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.84,0:00:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.31,0:00:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我们的痛苦都抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.28,0:00:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.85,0:01:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是士兵不是站着就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.32,0:01:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.85,0:01:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.49,0:01:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它们留给审判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.43,0:01:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.10,0:01:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牺牲的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.70,0:01:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只能奋起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.90,0:01:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻壳机动队 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.05,0:01:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颓废和复兴共存的城市  柏林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.89,0:01:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是第三次核大战以及第四次非核大战时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.16,0:01:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少数两度成为飞弹攻击目标的国际都市之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.47,0:01:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是这个对日耳曼民族有着特殊意义的城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.30,0:01:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次都会进行彻底而激烈的复兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.01,0:01:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三次以这个国家首都的地位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.44,0:01:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前又在复苏当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.75,0:02:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#18  天使之诗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.97,0:02:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使「京RAY」的3003式热光学迷彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.78,0:02:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是无法瞒过狗的嗅觉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特  你在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.42,0:02:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贪玩会吃大亏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.52,0:02:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知不觉就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.85,0:02:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本来就不适合这种长时间的监视任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.06,0:02:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上这些雪也很糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.69,0:02:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会提高光学迷彩的识别值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.56,0:02:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本就没有多少人适合做如此严酷的监视任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早点搞定回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.84,0:03:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于这点几天内就会有结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特  我要挂断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.08,0:03:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是密码通讯也不保证不会被窃听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点回到工作岗位上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.97,0:03:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里的寒冷就算切断感觉器官还是会有影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能赶上真不简单啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,台湾有直航班机吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.22,0:03:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先绕道香港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后要他们空出最早的班机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.32,0:03:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  我很吃惊这么大的猎物竟然派混编队伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.20,0:04:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听课长说任务内容的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一瞬间还怀疑是假情报呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓“天使之羽”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.11,0:04:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乃是以往只以工业国峰会\N为目标的超重量级恐怖分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至于会变成这种作战型态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.32,0:04:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,理由多半是要把功劳分给各国吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.65,0:04:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  直接指名我跟你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个时机恰巧的国外任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.56,0:04:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很自然就会想到是内厅推荐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么  开始说明这次的作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先请大家看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个男人名叫安杰里克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.25,0:04:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全身义体  自称是代理商
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,国籍为荷兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  因为某个事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.45,0:05:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们判定这个男子就是单独犯案\N造成史上最多牺牲者的恐怖分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.73,0:05:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位也非常熟悉的“天使之羽”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有确实证据吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.83,0:05:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您说的某个事件是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来依序说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.11,0:05:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“天使之羽”的犯罪思想和风格具有一贯性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.41,0:05:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他反对一小撮的先进国家独占全球的意志决定权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,预告要在举办峰会的国家某处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.05,0:05:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸掉一栋玻璃帷幕大楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.76,0:05:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于爆炸时大量玻璃碎片掉落造成许多牺牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以替他取了这个名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.70,0:05:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主办各国当然布下了严密的警戒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.37,0:05:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,设法处理这个事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.57,0:05:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是面对连在国内何处发生\N都不得而知的炸弹恐怖袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能全部阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.61,0:05:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此调查当局从被炸毁大楼的IR记录上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想要找出那家伙的长相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.38,0:06:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他是全身义体  每次都会改变长相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为完全不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是“天使之羽”的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.76,0:06:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为何一次也没有列入调查名单的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.36,0:06:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那现在为什么会知道他是全身义体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事实上两个月前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.94,0:06:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荷兰籍的义体医师为一名男子做义体换装手术时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.54,0:06:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失手让患者陷入意识不清的状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果发现几笔让人怀疑这个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.85,0:06:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否就是“天使之羽”的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.65,0:06:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据这名荷兰籍医师所说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从当时抽出的记忆当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.93,0:06:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这名男子过去做的炸弹恐怖袭击的细节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.83,0:06:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有每次更换义体的面部资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都一笔接一笔出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.57,0:06:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能从爆炸现场的记录确认出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.44,0:06:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟那个面部资料一致的人物吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.21,0:06:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部都找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.45,0:07:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荷兰籍医师在伦理和道德之间烦恼好几天之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通知了当地的警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果更早一点通报的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.32,0:07:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然没错  不过我们不能怪他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前的状况已经了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.16,0:07:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但为什么不是在下个月将举行峰会的利兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.07,0:07:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是在柏林集合我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.41,0:07:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,调查当局将男子过去的面部资料\N跟全世界机场的IR系统比对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“天使之羽”在犯下恐怖炸弹袭击之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会绕到柏林这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.95,0:07:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后在两天前从提格国际机场出发到目的地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.39,0:07:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上海峰会是2028年2月17日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.70,0:07:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫斯科峰会是2029年11月25日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.91,0:08:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而巴黎峰会则是2030年7月13日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部都是两天前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.05,0:08:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知为何他在过去重复了3次相同的模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.52,0:08:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这对除了犯罪风格之外没有共通行动的“天使之羽”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.32,0:08:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以说是很少见的常态模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.46,0:08:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他进入柏林的路线呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那家伙因为某种理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在犯罪之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.10,0:08:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会绕到柏林来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.44,0:08:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此这次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.04,0:08:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也很有可能在峰会前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.07,0:08:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进入柏林并在这里停留数日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.21,0:08:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这段时间内使用的名字还有义体\N我们认为绝对跟这份资料相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.15,0:08:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这可以说是首次而且最大的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这段期间我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.12,0:08:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论如何要找到并逮捕这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.73,0:08:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果找人的方法就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.80,0:09:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是让我想要放弃不干的任务啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总觉得跟狗八字不合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.32,0:09:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是那个女孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.22,0:09:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么晚了总是一个人到哪里去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还在大雪当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是本部的定时联络
