Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此外无异常情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.37,0:10:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,D－2  尚未确认目标
