Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本部了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各队员请继续监视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.63,0:10:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论是哭是笑  本作战还有两天就结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.17,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果“天使之羽”没有出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.10,0:10:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作战就由利兹当局接手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.40,0:10:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们又得回去调查那个\N到底是谁都不知道的恐怖分子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请认真执行任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要让这次的机会逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.14,0:10:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.85,0:10:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,D－4  你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.55,0:10:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是不适合我的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.75,0:11:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在车站和机场目击到透明的怪物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.62,0:11:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来不只我一个人觉得无聊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.23,0:11:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚洲难民在日本出岛公布自治区宣言？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.04,0:11:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情好像变得很棘手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个女孩是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,注意到我的存在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我想不到有什么理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.96,0:12:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使大人  为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.73,0:12:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邮件明明两个礼拜前就已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么爸爸还没有出现呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.73,0:12:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.71,0:13:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我感觉到有人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.15,0:13:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定有什么其它事情对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.99,0:13:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的感觉那么敏锐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.56,0:13:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.05,0:13:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,育幼院？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是从这里看到我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.81,0:14:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.81,0:14:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我总是跟爸爸说没有想要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  这次我有想要的东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.25,0:14:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想爸爸这次也会用不同的义体回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.49,0:14:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我来说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.16,0:15:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泰瑞莎  下来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.96,0:15:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.25,0:15:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两个礼拜内去见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.42,0:15:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在平常那间教堂碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.52,0:15:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有具体的日期吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.97,0:15:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我偷看一点点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好难看懂的字啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.69,0:16:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2030年7月12日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚上爸爸来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在教会的礼拜堂见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.33,0:16:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2029年11月24日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.37,0:16:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸照约定回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提早一个月的圣诞节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.30,0:16:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在教会的礼拜堂收到的礼物是喀什米尔羊毛外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.31,0:16:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2028年2月11日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸突然跟我联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在教会的礼拜堂见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.79,0:16:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿到连指手套当礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.43,0:16:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部都是安杰里克离开柏林的前一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,见到换了义体的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.64,0:16:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不知道是爸爸 就对暗号:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.78,0:17:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“天使今天要去做什么呢”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.88,0:17:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“要去把天使的羽毛洒在世界上”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.59,0:17:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.75,0:17:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩的父亲是“天使之羽”？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.55,0:17:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是本部的定时联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.59,0:17:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,D地区各队员报告情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,D－1  尚未确认目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无潜伏的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,D－2  尚未确认目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无潜伏的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,D－3  尚未确认目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此外无异常情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.04,0:18:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,D－4  为什么换地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.54,0:18:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事  因为那里野狗太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.94,0:18:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3003式对狗的嗅觉也没效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.41,0:18:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换地点的时候要联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确认之后会给你指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.18,0:18:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.10,0:19:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来忏悔杀害了许多无罪的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.97,0:19:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.85,0:19:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安杰里克  我知道你就是“天使之羽”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,束手就擒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.59,0:19:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.02,0:19:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.06,0:19:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.86,0:19:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们有确实的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.33,0:19:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不然这里怎么会有警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.47,0:19:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算为了自以为是的想法夺走许多人的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是想当女儿的父亲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.17,0:19:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被你炸毁而使玻璃碎片落下的那个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.08,0:19:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也有等着礼物的小孩和母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.88,0:19:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是以为只有夺走这些人性命的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.02,0:19:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以装作没事的表情跟女儿见面\N那可就大错特错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.92,0:20:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然很遗憾  不过你应该无法再跟女儿见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.70,0:20:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.13,0:20:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认识我女儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有件事拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你认识我女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.41,0:20:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以帮我把那包东西交给她吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.51,0:20:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是她非常想要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然大发慈悲吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.29,0:21:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本来想在旁边看的  可是你太松懈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.99,0:21:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.12,0:21:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过  你怎么知道这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.63,0:21:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我毕竟不能像托古萨那样\N在你身上安装GHOST侵入锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.56,0:21:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以在视觉装置上装了东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.70,0:21:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.94,0:21:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为昨天密码通讯的时候你就很松懈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.18,0:21:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联络本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回收这家伙之后作战就结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后回日本去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.39,0:21:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.26,0:21:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是爸爸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.50,0:21:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚有很大的声音  发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.60,0:21:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.77,0:21:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你眼睛看不见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.77,0:21:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.17,0:22:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！ 是爸爸对吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.24,0:22:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.21,0:22:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.98,0:22:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸  我好害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.35,0:22:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.92,0:22:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在那里对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.53,0:22:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸  天使今天要去做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.17,0:22:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使今天要去做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.10,0:22:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.64,0:22:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.21,0:22:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.38,0:22:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.75,0:22:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里都去不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.58,0:23:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我体内行星和星星的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.22,0:23:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听着它们每一个都唱着同样宁静的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.79,0:23:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在现实当中从来没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.83,0:23:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样美丽的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.10,0:23:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有一点怀疑或恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.47,0:23:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到一个声音—醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.71,0:23:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字—然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.28,0:23:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省视自身—然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.42,0:23:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光随时都围绕着我—时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.62,0:23:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相  所有我需要
